                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, T</hi> 141). I produce a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction at this Court—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted Jan.</hi>, 1846; <hi rend="italic">confined six months</hi>)—he is the person.</p>
